==English==
=== Verb ===
'''peruse''' ('''perused''', '''perusing''')
# to examine or [[consider]] with care
# to read something completely (NOTE: almost no one uses the word this way, instead using it to express the opposite meaning: "to scan, or read through quickly")
#* I will sign the contract after I '''peruse''' the fine print.

